WEBVTT

00:00:29.458 --> 00:00:30.875
Angry.

00:00:31.333 --> 00:00:32.667
On fire.

00:00:34.375 --> 00:00:35.625
Numb.

00:00:36.500 --> 00:00:37.750
Disconnected.

00:00:39.167 --> 00:00:40.833
Perhaps all of the above.

00:00:42.958 --> 00:00:46.434
These messy and complicated feelings,

00:00:46.458 --> 00:00:48.667
they make total sense.

00:00:49.917 --> 00:00:53.708
I wish that someone
had said this to me 30 years ago.

00:00:54.792 --> 00:00:59.434
I was a college freshman
taking environmental studies,

00:00:59.458 --> 00:01:04.000
which is basically a semester
of really bad news